    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/wombats-city-hostel-london/hotel/london-gb.html",
    "name": "Wombat's City Hostel London",
    "detail": "Wombats City Hostel is a well located little hostel near the centre of London. It’s well located only a 10 minute walk from the station or a 20 minute walk to the Tower of London. I stayed in a 8 person dormitory which was clean and had modern facilities. I did appreciate that the storage locker as well as an ensuite bathroom were all part of the same room. The hostel also had a bar which provided good vibes at night for chilling and talking with other travellers. I spent most of my time in London out and used the hostel only as a place to sleep with the occasional conversation with a fellow Aussie. Would not hesitate to recommend this hostel to other people wishing to stay in London on a budget for a few nights. ",
